article.description: — Jailyn Ingram posted 22 points as Florida Atlantic rolled past Mobile 83-41 on Saturday.
article.headline: Ingram, Boyd send FAU past NAIA Mobile by 42 PTs
article.linkText: Ingram, Boyd send FAU past NAIA Mobile by 42 PTs
article.story: MOBILE, Ala. -- — Jailyn Ingram posted 22 points as Florida Atlantic rolled past Mobile 83-41 on Saturday. Nicholas Boyd had 17 points for Florida Atlantic (1-2). Darvin Jones had 7 points for the Rams. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
